What you need to know:

The Argentine, who is still in contract negotiations with Barcelona, was given permission to miss training on Friday by coach Ronald KoemanThe 33-year-old has already played 47 matches this season for Barca, scoring 38 goals, but his future at the club remains in doubt as he has been linked with a move to Manchester CityBarcelona's defeat by Celta Vigo on Sunday leaves them third in La Liga, seven points behind leaders Atletico Madrid and only two ahead of fourth-placed Sevilla